1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:35,310 --> 00:01:39,130
[Lost Identity]

3
00:01:42,930 --> 00:01:45,530
[Episode 39]

4
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,200
Keep up!

5
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,240
Their car is catching up.

6
00:02:04,450 --> 00:02:05,910
We can't escape like this.

7
00:02:07,530 --> 00:02:08,570
This is the only way

8
00:02:08,570 --> 00:02:10,500
to eliminate suspicion about you.

9
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,820
How's your injury?

10
00:02:12,810 --> 00:02:13,880
I'm fine.

11
00:02:14,830 --> 00:02:16,829
If I can’t make it to the pier in time,

12
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,220
tell Secretary Chen

13
00:02:18,410 --> 00:02:19,410
not to wait for me.

14
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,450
Absolutely not.

15
00:02:21,510 --> 00:02:24,240
You must wait for me in Yan'an, do you understand?

16
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,060
The journey ahead is dangerous.

17
00:02:58,579 --> 00:02:59,500
Take care,

18
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,750
Comrade Midnight.

19
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,400
Take care,

20
00:03:04,110 --> 00:03:05,280
Comrade Wild Grass.

21
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,470
Turn!

22
00:03:42,510 --> 00:03:43,340
Keep up!

23
00:04:13,810 --> 00:04:14,850
Qiushui,

24
00:04:15,610 --> 00:04:17,130
believe me,

25
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,490
I didn't make this decision impetuously.

26
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,760
Given the current situation,

27
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:22,600
this is the best choice we have.

28
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:30,680
Qiushui,

29
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:33,600
do you remember what you said

30
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,460
when Yunjie sacrificed himself?

31
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:38,600
You said that Yunjie's sacrifice was worth it

32
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,080
for the bigger picture.

33
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:42,800
Yunjie could do it, so can I.

34
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,150
Comrade Qin Moqing,

35
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:45,820
do you know what you are talking about?

36
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:47,220
I firmly oppose it.

37
00:04:48,890 --> 00:04:50,360
I will report this to the organization,

38
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,159
and they will make the decision.

39
00:04:55,409 --> 00:04:56,460
Qiushui,

40
00:04:57,790 --> 00:04:58,670
Ou Xiao'an was right.

41
00:04:58,670 --> 00:05:00,040
We don't have time.

42
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,970
We don't have time to hesitate.

43
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,150
The trial is tomorrow.

44
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:11,040
You must make this decision for the organization.

45
00:05:11,270 --> 00:05:12,320
Between Wild Grass

46
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,120
and Midnight,

47
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,800
we can only save one.

48
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,400
Comrade Qin Moqing,

49
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:33,909
your code name is Wild Grass.

50
00:06:34,610 --> 00:06:37,650
You have been undercover in Chongqing Station for 4 years

51
00:06:37,650 --> 00:06:39,070
and have excellently completed

52
00:06:39,070 --> 00:06:41,330
the tasks assigned by the organization.

53
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:45,020
Over the past 4 years,

54
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:48,670
you went to Burma with the Expeditionary Force,

55
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:50,540
rescued Ou Xiao'an,

56
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:55,690
and suppressed the outbreak of local epidemics.

57
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:58,960
You cooperated with our comrades

58
00:06:59,110 --> 00:07:01,970
and captured Japanese spies in Chongqing.

59
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:05,460
You withstood numerous investigations

60
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:06,950
by the NBIS.

61
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,190
You went to Guizhou,

62
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:11,750
captured Ohashi Kazuya,

63
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:17,650
and rescued Secretary Chen Ke,

64
00:07:17,860 --> 00:07:19,140
who is me.

65
00:07:19,590 --> 00:07:21,000
At the prisoner-of-war camp,

66
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,460
you exposed the collusion

67
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,830
between the NBIS and Ohashi

68
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:26,280
and halted

69
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:29,160
the implementation of the Cherry Blossom Project.

70
00:07:33,090 --> 00:07:34,000
Here,

71
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:37,280
on behalf of the Party and the organization,

72
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,400
I express

73
00:07:38,890 --> 00:07:41,490
the highest respect and affirmation for you.

74
00:07:53,970 --> 00:07:55,900
Have you caught up with Qin Moqing?

75
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:58,320
Block all the routes!

76
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,930
Set up checkpoints! And enforce martial law!

77
00:08:03,270 --> 00:08:04,530
What about Ou Xiao'an?

78
00:08:06,030 --> 00:08:07,750
Keep searching.

79
00:08:07,890 --> 00:08:10,150
Dead or alive, I must see him!

80
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,020
Vice Captain Li.

81
00:08:19,470 --> 00:08:20,600
Vice Captain Wen.

82
00:08:22,330 --> 00:08:24,590
Have you caught up with the good student?

83
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:26,720
The personnel from the station, the dock,

84
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:29,920
and the Operations Department have all been dispatched,

85
00:08:30,050 --> 00:08:31,450
but we haven’t found him.

86
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,809
And Ou Xiao'an?

87
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,190
No news yet.

88
00:08:39,450 --> 00:08:40,450
Vice Captain Wen,

89
00:08:41,150 --> 00:08:42,280
I'm afraid...

90
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:44,910
Mr. Wen.

91
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:45,830
Xiao'an?

92
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:48,640
What happened?

93
00:08:51,570 --> 00:08:53,170
You didn't catch up with her?

94
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:54,710
No.

95
00:08:54,740 --> 00:08:56,200
What about Director Shen?

96
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,910
He's fine.

97
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:01,580
What happened to you?

98
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:04,210
There were too many communists,

99
00:09:04,780 --> 00:09:07,310
and they were holding Director Shen hostage.

100
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:08,850
We needed to rescue him.

101
00:09:08,880 --> 00:09:11,080
We couldn't let Director Shen get hurt.

102
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,560
Qin Moqing

103
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:14,330
shot me.

104
00:09:15,170 --> 00:09:16,690
She's gone mad.

105
00:09:22,410 --> 00:09:23,340
Vice Captain Li,

106
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:26,160
please contact Director Shen

107
00:09:26,690 --> 00:09:27,530
and find out

108
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:29,490
if what he said is true.

109
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:43,080
Which way did the communists go?

110
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:45,170
From where we intercepted them,

111
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:48,070
it seems they headed northwest.

112
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:51,160
You may leave.

113
00:10:15,430 --> 00:10:17,230
Is this Operations Department?

114
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:34,260
Director Shen,

115
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,330
I couldn’t be reassured just by a phone call,

116
00:10:36,330 --> 00:10:37,930
so I came to see you in person.

117
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:39,640
I’m fine.

118
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,950
Qin Moqing

119
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:44,220
was shot by you.

120
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,670
In such deep water, she’s undoubtedly dead.

121
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,800
Let’s not mention Qin Moqing anymore.

122
00:10:50,270 --> 00:10:52,320
About Ohashi Kazuya,

123
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,630
what should we do?

124
00:10:56,830 --> 00:10:59,310
What’s the higher-ups' plan?

125
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:03,800
The Attendant Section has given the guidance.

126
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,230
Ohashi Kazuya must die.

127
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:07,030
No one can save him.

128
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,570
They’re particularly unhappy

129
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:13,750
about the fact that we helped Ohashi

130
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:15,090
fake his death before.

131
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:19,620
I've reported this long ago.

132
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,040
They’re pretending not to know.

133
00:11:24,370 --> 00:11:25,830
What about the Americans?

134
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,990
Didn’t they always want to save Ohashi?

135
00:11:29,640 --> 00:11:31,440
You can’t count on these people.

136
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,640
As soon as the court verdict was out,

137
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:35,440
they all showed up to condemn us,

138
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:37,000
accusing us of being schemers

139
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,130
who are colluding with war criminals.

140
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:43,390
Anyway,

141
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:47,590
people from the Attendant Section will be here tonight

142
00:11:47,590 --> 00:11:49,500
for the final interrogation of Ohashi.

143
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:50,260
Of course,

144
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:53,020
this will only be a formality.

145
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:55,870
Ohashi won’t say anything.

146
00:11:58,510 --> 00:11:59,680
But Li Shaotang,

147
00:12:01,430 --> 00:12:02,540
I must warn you,

148
00:12:05,470 --> 00:12:08,600
no matter what your relationship with Ohashi Kazuya is,

149
00:12:11,190 --> 00:12:12,230
you cannot

150
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,990
save him anymore.

151
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,880
Right now, I just hope

152
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,290
that his death

153
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:22,440
won’t implicate you.

154
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:30,930
I’m telling you, Li Shaotang,

155
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:32,150
the reason

156
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,320
you were not brought to military court

157
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,000
with Ohashi Kazuya

158
00:12:36,680 --> 00:12:38,470
was that your experiments

159
00:12:40,100 --> 00:12:41,830
were our ultimate weapon

160
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:43,430
against the Communists.

161
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,520
Do your job well as the Vice Captain.

162
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:55,950
Yes.

163
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,320
Secretary Chen, Ou Xiao'an is here.

164
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,780
Quickly, have him come in.

165
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:26,720
Secretary Chen,

166
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,860
I am Ou Xiao'an,

167
00:13:29,130 --> 00:13:30,440
a member of the Communist Party,

168
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:32,040
with the code name Midnight.

169
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:33,470
I am here to report to you.

170
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:34,880
Comrade Xiao'an.

171
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:38,870
Secretary Chen.

172
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,760
How is your health?

173
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:41,820
Much better.

174
00:13:41,850 --> 00:13:43,630
Secretary Chen, please have a seat.

175
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:44,080
You too.

176
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,760
Okay.

177
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:51,080
How is the situation in the Chongqing Station now?

178
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,390
Don't worry, Secretary Chen.

179
00:13:52,390 --> 00:13:55,480
The Chongqing Station didn’t find any evidence against me.

180
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,410
Secretary Chen,

181
00:13:56,870 --> 00:13:57,840
I'm here today

182
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,390
to ask

183
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,080
if Comrade Wild Grass is...

184
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:04,350
Don't worry.

185
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:06,000
I just received news

186
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:08,390
that she has been successfully rescued

187
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:09,560
by our comrades

188
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:12,880
and should now be on a ship leaving Chongqing.

189
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:15,270
That's great.

190
00:14:15,810 --> 00:14:17,110
I’m relieved.

191
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:19,200
Today, Comrade Li Manqiu and I

192
00:14:19,950 --> 00:14:21,190
are about to set off.

193
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:23,670
However,

194
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:27,510
it’s not safe for you to stay in Chongqing now.

195
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:28,990
I want you

196
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:31,080
to move with us

197
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:32,760
and leave Chongqing.

198
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:34,890
Secretary Chen,

199
00:14:35,430 --> 00:14:36,600
have a safe journey.

200
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,630
I can't leave yet.

201
00:14:39,230 --> 00:14:41,230
I still have many tasks to complete.

202
00:14:41,350 --> 00:14:43,600
Although Ohashi Kazuya has been brought to justice,

203
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:46,130
the NBIS is still conspiring with Li Shaotang

204
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,550
on biochemical weapons.

205
00:14:47,830 --> 00:14:48,440
This poses

206
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,970
a significant threat to us.

207
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:53,570
I never expected that,

208
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:58,190
despite knowing Li Shaotang is a Japanese spy,

209
00:14:58,790 --> 00:15:00,070
the NBIS

210
00:15:00,710 --> 00:15:01,910
still sheltered him

211
00:15:02,350 --> 00:15:04,510
and let him continue his biochemical experiments.

212
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,550
The CNP

213
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:07,390
is now resorting to all means

214
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:10,310
to counter us.

215
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:13,200
Your situation within the NBIS

216
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:14,770
is very dangerous.

217
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,030
Therefore,

218
00:15:17,070 --> 00:15:18,440
I do not support you

219
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:20,320
staying undercover.

220
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:23,240
I have ways.

221
00:15:23,510 --> 00:15:24,760
Qin Moqing and I

222
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,240
made this plan

223
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,480
to gain

224
00:15:27,590 --> 00:15:29,000
their trust in me.

225
00:15:29,170 --> 00:15:30,070
Besides,

226
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:32,440
I now have Shen Congwu to testify for me.

227
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:33,560
Secretary Chen,

228
00:15:34,470 --> 00:15:35,930
it’s not just about these.

229
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:38,840
The large number of gas bombs from 810

230
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:41,270
must be hidden somewhere in Chongqing.

231
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,520
I need to find out where they are.

232
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:44,790
Don't worry.

233
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,870
Well,

234
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:50,000
the organization will make other arrangements.

235
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:52,350
You'd better move with us.

236
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,120
Secretary Chen.

237
00:15:56,820 --> 00:15:57,710
Yan'an

238
00:15:58,820 --> 00:16:00,550
doesn't lack a soldier like me.

239
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:03,240
However, Yan'an definitely needs

240
00:16:04,040 --> 00:16:06,510
an intelligence officer inside the Chongqing NBIS

241
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:08,240
with firsthand intelligence.

242
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,170
Secretary Chen,

243
00:16:10,670 --> 00:16:11,630
I request

244
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:13,440
to stay undercover.

245
00:16:19,070 --> 00:16:20,000
Secretary Chen,

246
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,530
please don’t hesitate any longer.

247
00:16:22,830 --> 00:16:25,170
We’ve made it through all these years.

248
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:26,590
When we were in 810,

249
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:27,830
you told me

250
00:16:28,110 --> 00:16:29,640
that beyond the high walls,

251
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:32,390
there are countless comrades

252
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,830
with the same goal

253
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,270
and dream as ours:

254
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,200
to strive tirelessly

255
00:16:38,990 --> 00:16:40,230
for China,

256
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:43,030
for a new China that is prosperous,

257
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,400
free from oppression, and where people live

258
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,590
and work in peace.

259
00:16:49,260 --> 00:16:50,870
This has also been my goal

260
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,540
for all these years.

261
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:53,830
Secretary Chen,

262
00:16:54,190 --> 00:16:56,390
let me continue to uphold this mission.

263
00:16:56,460 --> 00:16:57,780
Let me complete my mission

264
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:58,700
for the Party

265
00:16:59,080 --> 00:17:00,850
and the people.

266
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,750
Comrade Xiao'an,

267
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:18,630
Comrade Lou Mingyuan was right about you.

268
00:17:18,930 --> 00:17:20,380
We'll be waiting for your

269
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:22,089
victorious return.

270
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:23,599
Secretary Chen,

271
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,609
victory is just around the corner.

272
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:29,190
We'll soon see the dawn.

273
00:17:44,550 --> 00:17:45,150
Open the door.

274
00:17:45,150 --> 00:17:45,830
Yes.

275
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:53,390
Ohashi Kazuya,

276
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:55,800
Judge Randal from America is here to see you.

277
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,260
I don't want to see anyone.

278
00:17:58,480 --> 00:17:59,360
Mr. Ohashi.

279
00:17:59,420 --> 00:18:00,440
Your Honor,

280
00:18:01,150 --> 00:18:02,760
the trial is over.

281
00:18:03,470 --> 00:18:04,950
Why have you come to see me?

282
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:06,310
Mr. Ohashi,

283
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,600
you know

284
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,950
that our stance with the National Government

285
00:18:09,950 --> 00:18:11,030
is to protect you.

286
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:13,640
It was those communists

287
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:15,670
who secretly exposed your identity

288
00:18:15,670 --> 00:18:17,270
that led to this outcome.

289
00:18:17,840 --> 00:18:18,790
Leave.

290
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:21,840
I'll die anyway.

