What happened to him?

583
00:35:01,970 --> 00:35:04,080
Li Shaotang committed treason.

584
00:35:04,510 --> 00:35:06,640
The station has already arrested him.

585
00:35:09,570 --> 00:35:11,030
What?

586
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:14,570
It was that Japanese, Ohashi Kazuya, who identified him.

587
00:35:14,570 --> 00:35:15,930
He said Li Shaotang

588
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:17,340
was a Japanese spy

589
00:35:17,340 --> 00:35:19,590
planted in our Chongqing Station.

590
00:35:29,250 --> 00:35:31,850
Li Shaotang has already admitted in court

591
00:35:33,930 --> 00:35:35,290
that he personally

592
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,960
killed Vice Captain Feng.

593
00:36:13,160 --> 00:36:14,150
Jingxian,

594
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:16,450
I promise you

595
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:19,310
that our wedding will proceed as planned.

596
00:36:19,370 --> 00:36:20,530
By then,

597
00:36:20,690 --> 00:36:22,810
you'll be the happiest bride ever.

598
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:27,230
Marry me.

599
00:36:35,410 --> 00:36:36,390
Everyone,

600
00:36:36,550 --> 00:36:38,070
it won't be long

601
00:36:38,250 --> 00:36:39,470
before the war ends.

602
00:36:39,550 --> 00:36:41,480
And we will win this war.

603
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:43,190
Just as Ms. Feng said,

604
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:45,030
everyone can go home

605
00:36:45,150 --> 00:36:46,670
safely and peacefully

606
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,860
and reunite with their families.

607
00:36:49,230 --> 00:36:50,320
I, Li Shaotang,

608
00:36:50,390 --> 00:36:52,990
am certainly a person loyal to the Kuomintang.

609
00:36:57,280 --> 00:36:58,610
I will publish this in the newspaper.

610
00:36:58,610 --> 00:37:00,280
I want everyone to know

611
00:37:00,350 --> 00:37:03,080
that Feng Yunian’s daughter is getting married.

612
00:37:11,160 --> 00:37:14,230
Bride and groom, please exchange rings.

613
00:37:23,500 --> 00:37:25,230
Dad! Dad!

614
00:37:25,330 --> 00:37:26,900
Dad, what happened to you?

615
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:57,560
Come in.

616
00:37:59,120 --> 00:37:59,960
Mr. Wen.

617
00:38:01,470 --> 00:38:02,280
Xiao'an.

618
00:38:02,820 --> 00:38:04,370
Take some people from the Operations Department

619
00:38:04,370 --> 00:38:05,410
to Qin's Mansion.

620
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:13,440
[Search Warrant]

621
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:19,660
The entire NBIS knows

622
00:38:19,750 --> 00:38:20,720
that you and Qin Moqing

623
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:22,670
are my two prized students.

624
00:38:25,990 --> 00:38:28,990
I must have been blind not to see through her.

625
00:38:29,700 --> 00:38:32,460
You ended up in a direct confrontation.

626
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,080
What about you?

627
00:38:44,330 --> 00:38:45,530
I'll do it right away.

628
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,860
This is your lifetime’s savings.

629
00:39:12,630 --> 00:39:13,690
Don't you feel sad?

630
00:39:16,390 --> 00:39:18,320
Better to be a dog in peaceful times

631
00:39:18,730 --> 00:39:20,390
than a human in chaotic times.

632
00:39:21,510 --> 00:39:23,590
I had already anticipated this day.

633
00:39:24,750 --> 00:39:26,590
You have a good mindset.

634
00:39:28,710 --> 00:39:30,840
Have you read "The Story of the Stone"?

635
00:39:31,880 --> 00:39:33,860
"Like birds who, having fed, to the woods repair,

636
00:39:33,860 --> 00:39:36,580
They leave the landscape desolate and bare."

637
00:39:40,970 --> 00:39:43,250
Even if I were immensely wealthy,

638
00:39:44,050 --> 00:39:46,510
there would still be a day when it's all gone.

639
00:39:48,830 --> 00:39:50,830
You’ve brought this on yourself.

640
00:39:50,970 --> 00:39:52,570
You can’t blame anyone else.

641
00:39:53,650 --> 00:39:54,580
Yes.

642
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:58,310
I know I’m a fat piece of meat.

643
00:39:58,700 --> 00:40:00,960
Everyone who sees me wants to take a bite.

644
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:02,990
The Japanese,

645
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:04,550
Wang Jingwei,

646
00:40:04,570 --> 00:40:05,740
your NBIS,

647
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,480
and those Americans—

648
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:10,140
none of them can be relied on in the end.

649
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:12,600
Once they had taken all the meat off my bones,

650
00:40:12,850 --> 00:40:14,300
they naturally left.

651
00:40:14,910 --> 00:40:16,600
I know

652
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:18,620
that I’ve gained wealth and benefits

653
00:40:18,620 --> 00:40:19,970
by selling my dignity and integrity,

654
00:40:19,970 --> 00:40:21,700
which is not worth mentioning.

655
00:40:22,980 --> 00:40:25,300
But I raised a wonderful sister.

656
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:27,400
Qin Moqing is exceptional

657
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:30,710
and the priceless treasure of our family.

658
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:32,820
Thinking of her

659
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:35,350
brings me peace of mind.

660
00:40:40,130 --> 00:40:41,650
My sister was right.

661
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:46,320
This world can be changed.

662
00:41:01,010 --> 00:41:02,960
You did raise a good sister.

663
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:06,130
Here’s the deal.

664
00:41:07,790 --> 00:41:08,990
I’ll give you

665
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,320
two hours.

666
00:41:12,100 --> 00:41:13,360
It's up to you to decide

667
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,610
how we'll do it.

668
00:41:47,340 --> 00:41:48,220
Captain Chen.

669
00:41:49,200 --> 00:41:50,530
It's me, Ou Xiao'an.

670
00:41:51,230 --> 00:41:52,470
Let me ask you.

671
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:55,090
Where will the batch of gas bombs from Wulong

672
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:56,800
be sent to be destroyed?

673
00:42:01,750 --> 00:42:02,520
Okay.

674
00:42:03,470 --> 00:42:05,000
Take me there to have a look.

675
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,110
Okay.

676
00:42:11,770 --> 00:42:12,720
Slowly.

677
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:14,670
Easy, easy.

678
00:42:19,390 --> 00:42:20,200
Hurry up.

679
00:42:24,570 --> 00:42:25,690
Easy.

680
00:42:27,610 --> 00:42:28,610
Be careful.

681
00:42:34,470 --> 00:42:35,450
Who are you?

682
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:37,180
This is a military restricted area. Entry is prohibited.

683
00:42:37,180 --> 00:42:39,850
This is Section Chief Ou from the Chongqing Station of the NBIS.

684
00:42:39,850 --> 00:42:41,720
He is here on the orders of Captain Wei from the Chongqing Station

685
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:44,280
to inspect today's gas bomb destruction operation.

686
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:46,530
I did receive news that someone from the NBIS would be here to inspect.

687
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:48,990
However, please present your credentials.

688
00:42:49,590 --> 00:42:50,630
We’re here to check on

689
00:42:50,630 --> 00:42:52,110
the gas bomb destruction.

690
00:42:51,990 --> 00:42:53,120
[Name: Ou Xiao'an]

691
00:42:58,390 --> 00:42:58,990
Come in, please.

692
00:42:58,990 --> 00:42:59,600
Okay.

693
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:03,290
These are the gas bombs to be destroyed today.

694
00:43:03,950 --> 00:43:07,150
Over there is the chloramine solution destruction pool.

695
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:08,840
How many boxes are there in total?

696
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:10,000
140 boxes.

697
00:43:10,420 --> 00:43:11,510
Ten bombs per box.

698
00:43:11,530 --> 00:43:12,730
A total of 1400 bombs.

699
00:43:14,890 --> 00:43:16,550
Why aren't you wearing protective equipment

700
00:43:16,550 --> 00:43:18,390
for destroying the gas bombs?

701
00:43:18,950 --> 00:43:20,060
Before the official destruction,

702
00:43:20,060 --> 00:43:21,350
wearing that is inconvenient for the work.

703
00:43:21,350 --> 00:43:21,920
We’ll put it on shortly.

704
00:43:21,920 --> 00:43:22,760
Open it and let me take a look.

705
00:43:22,760 --> 00:43:23,510
Open it.

706
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:29,120
Open the ones at the back too.
